The Postmaster of Mafdet has an open commission for a complete route survey of the Scorching Sands. The Sands form a critical corridor on routes operating south and east of Mafdet, and no comprehensive navigation record exists in the harbor authority's reference files. Survey every accessible section of the Scorching Sands and return with a complete route record.
Your Scorching Sands survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority. The completed record has been added to the southern corridor reference files, and convoy operators registered for desert routes have been notified of the newly available documentation.
